title: The Amazing Ohio Challenge Cyclocross Race
description: A light-hearted event, a Cyclocross race in front of 20,000 specatators at the Ohio Challenge Hot Air Balloon  Festival. Fifteen teams of 3 persons each will complete a 1 km cyclocross time trial.  TT times will be used to ability-match racers for A, B and C mass start cyclocross events immediately following the TT.  Team Prizes to the top 3 teams.  The event is a promo for the Ohio Valley Cyclocross Cup Championship and Java Johnny\\\'s Lionhearts Cyclocross Race. A fetival atmosphere with food, music, and many hot air balloons.
course: A rolling grass / paved loop about 1 km in length in front of a huge festival crowd.  Festival information, maps and directions can be found at www.ohiochallenge.com
registration: Pre-register your team by phone or email.  513-403-1951, ddobrozsi @cinci.rr.com; Required information: Team name. Major Sponsor Names.  Hometown of Team.  Name, address, phone and email of each of the 3 team racers PLUS one additional, backup racer.  Due by July 10th
notes: All categories are invited to participate.  Ability matching before the mass start races mean you will race against closely matched racers.
